Lemon pepper lobster tails are my favorite go-to  recipe when i really don’t feel like cooking- but wanna look like i made something fancy😂😂😂🔥🥵🦞🤷🏽‍♀️Heres the recipe below:
2  lobster tails (6 oz) 
2 tsp Chef Bae Garlic Butter
2 tsp fresh lemon juice
1 tsp lemon pepper seasoning 
1 tsp Chef Bae Seafood Seasoning 
White rice (or rice pilaf)
1 pound of Broccolini 
1/2 tsp Balsamic vinegar 
1-2 tsp Olive oil 
1/8 tsp Chef Bae Pink Salt 
A pinch of Pepper 

Click the link in my bio💜

Use code “YouFeelMe” for 20% off everything on the website🔥 The link is in my bio or visit www.CuttinUpWithBae.com
